message:
Replaces system-dependent line separator by %n in printf

Signed-off-by: Manoel Campos <manoelcampos@gmail.com>

added: "\tVm %2d: Host's CPU utilization: %5.0f%% | Host's RAM utilization: %5.0f%% | Host's BW utilization: %5.0f%%%n",
deleted: "\tVm %2d: Host's CPU utilization: %5.0f%% | Host's RAM utilization: %5.0f%% | Host's BW utilization: %5.0f%%\n",
